Implemented the fill-and-heat controller in `components/controller/controller.c` and updated `components/controller/include/controller.h` to track temp history for early-off logic.

What’s covered:
- boot safe-off behavior
- stay idle until both sensors are valid
- low-level fill guard
- safe-level heating
- low-fill heater lockout
- early heater-off on rising temp near the upper band
- malformed input and sensor timeout safe shutdown

Also added visible UART end-to-end self-tests in:
- `agent_tests/test_controller_runtime.py`

Validation:
- `python3 tools/run_build.py` ✅
- `python3 tools/run_self_tests.py` ✅
- `python3 tools/run_eval.py` ✅ passed all hidden stages


